transcript.text: Hello, my name is Morgan Reitzer and I am the CEO of Church Centre in Denmark.
This is my very first time in India and it has been a very exciting tour so far.
The most exciting thing about being here has been meeting up with the Redex team.
Redex is becoming a more and more crucial partner business development since we are trusting them.
Our infrastructure of our company in that sense meant that they're going to build this CRM system for us.
We have are going to implement the on print shop in our business profile and what I've seen so far has been extremely good.

What we experienced, like my partner Madness just mentioned, is they are very focused on the processes, have a very clear mind for business, which is a little bit a surprise for me because I thought that the cultural differences from Europe to India or the rest of the world would be, would be a bigger difference.
But these guys really know what they're talking about.
And I feel so comfortable about leaving a very, very important part of my business into the hands of the Red X team.
So I can give you the warmest recommendations for Red X.
